Name: ovarian dysgenesis 1
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in homozygous or compound heterozygous mutation in the gene encoding follicle-stimulating hormone receptor on chromosome 2p16.

Name: ovarian dysgenesis 2
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in mutation in the BMP15 gene on chromosome Xp11.

Name: ovarian dysgenesis 3
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in homozygous mutation in the PSMC3IP gene on chromosome 17q12-q21.

Name: ovarian dysgenesis 4
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in homozygous mutation in the MCM9 gene on chromosome 6q22.

Name: ovarian dysgenesis 5
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in homozygous mutation in the SOHLH1 gene on chromosome 9q34.

Name: ovarian dysgenesis 6
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in homozygous mutation in the NUP107 gene on chromosome 12q15.

Name: ovarian dysgenesis 7
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in homozygous mutation in the MRPS22 gene on chromosome 3q23.

Name: ovarian dysgenesis 8
Definition: A 46 XX gonadal dysgenesis that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the ESR2 gene on chromosome 14q23.
